Package: landisbc
Type: Package
Title: British Columbia Study-Area Tools for LANDIS-II Workflows
Description: Province of British Columbia data-preparation helpers for
    'LANDIS-II' forest-landscape simulation workflows -- e.g. deriving observed
    fire-severity distributions from provincial burn-severity data for Dynamic
    Fire calibration, and translating Vegetation Resource Inventory ('VRI')
    polygons into 'LANDIS-II' initial-communities maps + CSVs. Companion to
    'landisutils' (the study-area-agnostic 'LANDIS-II' tooling); BC-specific
    data sources and mappings live here so they can be reused across British
    Columbia projects.
URL: https://github.com/FOR-CAST/landisbc
BugReports: https://github.com/FOR-CAST/landisbc/issues
Version: 0.0.2
